    {
        " layer to create a chemical change that generates the patterns for the circuit.     Etching is the next process that is required. The part of the silicon that was not covered by the ": null
    },
    {
        "photoresist": "Photoresist"
    },
    {
        " layer from the previous step can now be etched. The main process typically used today is called ": null
